Package cs699_a2021.invertedstack.reviewsx

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MainActivity
    MainActivity for the app This activity will fetch names of the conferences, years and categories from the server and show the options On clicking any of the conference items [name, year, category], `PaperList` activity will start showing the list of papers in that particular category for that year in that conference
    NoteTakingActivity
    This activity is responsible for actually taking notes The activity contains an instance of `markwon` library that handles the markdown The activity also implements a nice animated live editor for markdown
    PaperList
    This activity is responsible for displaying the list of papers for a particular category for a particular year of a particular conference
    PaperWithDiscussion
    This activity shows a particular paper info along with it's discussion (i.e.
    ViewCollectionActivity
    View a particular collection of papers.
